<subSubSection id="C337088DF77BB13AB182FCBC30D447E3" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F77BB13AB182FCBC32C0473C" blockId="14.[151,1437,727,1221]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535">
<collectionCode id="ED3CC3C3F77BB13AB182FCBC32C24018" box="[199,251,835,861]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535">TYPE</collectionCode>
MATERIAL: 
<bibRefCitation id="EFBC26F7F77BB13AB03DFCBC305F401F" author="Sundevall, C. J." box="[376,614,834,861]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" pagination="96 - 111" refId="ref29984" refString="Sundevall, C. J. (1850) Foglar fran sodra Afrika. Ofversigt af Kongliga Vetenskaps-akademiens forhandlingar, 7 (4), 96 - 111." type="journal article" year="1850">Sundevall (1850: 98)</bibRefCitation>
gives no indication that his original description was based on more than 
<specimenCount id="9D2B908FF77BB13AB1D2FC98330F40C3" box="[151,310,871,897]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
. According to Sundevall’s acquisition catalogue the actual type series consisted of 
<specimenCount id="9D2B908FF77BB13AB5B3FC9837A040C3" box="[1270,1433,871,897]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" type="generic">six specimens</specimenCount>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFBC26F7F77BB13AB1D2FC74339340E7" author="Gyldenstolpe, N." box="[151,426,907,933]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" pagination="1 - 116" refId="ref28755" refString="Gyldenstolpe, N. (1926) Types of birds in the Royal Natural History Museum in Stockholm. Arkiv f or Zoologi, 19, 1 - 116." type="journal article" year="1926">Gyldenstolpe (1926: 10)</bibRefCitation>
referred to NRM 568693 [6127] as a “type”, which we treat as a 
<typeStatus id="5496E5A4F77BB13AB5CBFC7436CC40E7" box="[1166,1269,907,933]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535">lectotype</typeStatus>
designation of this adult male collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F77BB13AB0EBFC503077408B" box="[430,590,943,969]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" value="1840-04-26">
26 April 
<quantity id="4CD5F6E3F77BB13AB353FC503077408B" box="[534,590,943,969]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.6736" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" unit="in" value="1840.0">1840</quantity>
</date>
in Durban. The 
<specimenCount id="9D2B908FF77BB13AB255FC5031DE408B" box="[784,999,943,969]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" type="generic" typeStatus="paralectotypes">five paralectotypes</specimenCount>
are: NRM 523061 [6128], a mounted female collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F77BB13AB025FC2C303A40AF" box="[352,515,979,1005]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" value="1840-04-26">
26 April 
<quantity id="4CD5F6E3F77BB13AB08DFC2C303A40AF" box="[456,515,979,1005]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.6736" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" unit="in" value="1840.0">1840</quantity>
</date>
in Durban; NRM 545587 [6129], an unsexed juvenile collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F77BB13AB5BCFC2C37A540AF" box="[1273,1436,979,1005]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" value="1840-04-26">
26 April 
<quantity id="4CD5F6E3F77BB13AB424FC2C37A540AF" box="[1377,1436,979,1005]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.6736" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" unit="in" value="1840.0">1840</quantity>
</date>
in Durban; NRM 545586 [6324], a female collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F77BB13AB3B2FC0831994753" box="[759,928,1015,1041]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" value="1840-08-04">4 August 1840</date>
(label) or 
<date id="FF937DC6F77BB13AB55DFC0836DF4753" box="[1048,1254,1015,1041]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" value="1841-02-20">20 February 1841</date>
(old catalogue) in Durban; a male [6323], probably collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F77BB13AB3FBFBE4316F4777" box="[702,854,1051,1077]" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" value="1841-02-20">
20 Feb 
<quantity id="4CD5F6E3F77BB13AB25EFBE4316F4777" box="[795,854,1051,1077]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.67614" pageId="14" pageNumber="535" unit="in" value="1841.0">1841</quantity>
</date>
in Durban, sent on exchange to Leiden in 1850; and a juvenile [6325] with uncertain data, sent on exchange to 
<collectingRegion id="49E995E4F77BB13AB23DFBC031FB471B" box="[888,962,1087,1113]" country="Germany" name="Berlin" pageId="14" pageNumber="535">Berlin</collectingRegion>
in 1853 (but not found in the ZMB collection).
</paragraph>
